## HARD CONSTRAINTS — NEVER VIOLATE

| # | Constraint |
|---|-----------|
| 1 | Single HTML file. No external files. No imports. |
| 2 | Zero external dependencies. No CDN. No frameworks. No Google Fonts. |
| 3 | Mobile-first. 75%+ traffic is mobile on 3G/4G. |
