## DATA — COMMUNE_DATA

### Data Quality Rules (ENFORCE ON EVERY GENERATED PAGE)
1. Every commune name must be **pure Arabic only** — no Latin, Chinese, or numeric characters
2. No duplicate commune within the same wilaya
3. The new wilayas 59-69 contain communes transferred from parent wilayas — use official ONS source
4. If unsure about specific communes, prefer "اكتبي اسم بلديتك في العنوان" fallback option for that wilaya
5. Validate dataset entry count: total across all wilayas must equal 1541

